OL,3,CDeath of man who fell after railings
OL,4,Ccollapsed probed as corporate
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FThe death of a man who fell from a
OL,8,Fflat after balcony railings gave way
OL,9,Fis being investigated as corporate
OL,10,Fmanslaughter by police, a pre-inquest
OL,11,Freview heard.
OL,13,FJoshua Robbins, 23, had ordered a
OL,14,Ftakeaway pizza to his flat at Holland
OL,15,Fand Thurston Dwellings, in Holborn,
OL,16,Fcentral London, to share with his
OL,17,Ffather and leant on the railings of
OL,18,Fhis balcony to check on the delivery
OL,19,Fwhen they are said to have collapsed
OL,20,Fon January 29.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
