OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784657907
OL,3,CDeath of man who fell after railings
OL,4,Ccollapsed probed as corporate
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FWill Robbins, 49, watched his son fall
OL,8,Fto his death.
OL,10,FThe Metropolitan Police is carrying
OL,11,Fout a corporate manslaughter
OL,12,Finvestigation and Islington and
OL,13,FShoreditch Housing Association is
OL,14,Fcomplying with requests for material,
OL,15,Fa pre-inquest review heard on Tuesday.
OL,17,FThe force is liaising with the Crown
OL,18,FProsecution Service, St Pancras
OL,19,FCoroner's Court heard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784657907
OL,3,CDeath of man who fell after railings
OL,4,Ccollapsed probed as corporate
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Mark Paterson said
OL,8,Fthe scene of Mr Robbins's death was
OL,9,Fexamined at the time and a forensic
OL,10,Fengineer attended, and CCTV has been
OL,11,Fobtained.
OL,13,FDI Paterson said: "It's an ongoing
OL,14,Finvestigation, a lot of the material
OL,15,Fis held by ISHA who are fully
OL,16,Fcompliant with requests that are being
OL,17,Fmade at this stage."
OL,26,@uD@SOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
