OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784657907
OL,3,CDeath of man who fell after railings
OL,4,Ccollapsed probed as corporate
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,F"I thought 'oh well, if I get a reply
OL,8,Fit would just be your bog standard,
OL,9,Fwritten by someone else (response) and
OL,10,Fhe just won't even know that it's gone
OL,11,Fout', but the fact that he wrote it so
OL,12,Fhe actually signed it himself at the
OL,13,Fbottom and wrote a little bit extra,
OL,14,Fit did seem really genuine.
OL,16,F"When I showed Will, he was just like
OL,17,F'oh my god the prime minister knows
OL,18,Fwho our son was'.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
