CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784657907
OL,3,CDeath of man who fell after railings
OL,4,Ccollapsed probed as corporate
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,F"I said I'd even write to the King if
OL,8,FI had to. The point is that he did
OL,9,Fmatter, and he does matter, and
OL,10,Feveryone's child should matter."
OL,12,FA Met Police spokesperson said: "At
OL,13,Fthis time our investigation remains
OL,14,Fongoing, and we continue to liaise
OL,15,Fwith the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,16,Fwhile enquiries continue.
OL,18,F"These enquiries can take some time
OL,19,Fgiven the nature of the investigation
OL,20,Fand complexities.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@`O]tD@aOUzD@AOU
